Application - Application is a set of programs which are used to perform a particular task.
or we can say that.
"We use application to make our work easier and faster".

   Types of Applications:
-> Stand alone application.
-> Web Application.
-> Client server/ web application.

(1) Stand alone application --> Those applications which are installed in a computer and only single person can use of it at a time is called stand alone application.
                                Example: Suppose today i have drawn a painting in the software paint and saved that painting as a "FirstPainting". Now the painting is saved in my hard drive disk. now if i want to open that painting in my friend's laptop which was saved in my laptop the i am not able to findmy painting because it is present in my hard drive.
                              * So in stand alone application the data is stored is local to user.
                                Examples : Paint, Adobe photoshop, notepad etc.    
(2) Web Application --> Those application which can be accessed through browser using an internet connection is called web application.
